question.en:
What is the output of this dynamic programming code?
python
def fib(n, memo={}):
    if n in memo:
        return memo[n]
    if n <= 1:
        return n
    memo[n] = fib(n - 1, memo) + fib(n - 2, memo)
    return memo[n]

print(fib(5))

